<li>Co-organizer with P. Hofstra and J.Funk of the Fields Institute sponsored <a href="http://www.fields.utoronto.ca/programs/scientific/09-10/semigroups/index.html">Workshop on Semigroups and Categories</a>, Ottawa, May 2010.</li>
