<li>Co-organizer with R. Grigorchuk and Z. Sunik of <a href="http://www.birs.ca/birspages.php?task=displayevent&event_id=08w5066">Self-Similarity and Branching in Group Theory</a>, Banff, October 2008.</li>
<li>Co-organizer with E. Neher and V. Dlab of the Fields Institute sponsored <a href="http://www.fields.utoronto.ca/programs/scientific/08-09/algebraweek/">Algebra Week</a>, September 2008.</li> 
<li>Lex Renner and I organized a special session, entitled <a href="http://math.ca/Events/winter07/sessions_scientific">Algebraic Combinatorics, Representations and Geometry</a>, of the Winter 2007 Meeting of the Canadian Mathematical Society.</li> 
<li>Inna Bumagin and I are organized a <a
 href="http://www.fields.utoronto.ca/programs/scientific/06-07/group_theory/">Workshop  
on Geometric Methods in Group Theory</a> sponsored by <a
