 conference will take place from August 16-19.</li>
  <li>Luis Ribes and I organized in August 2005 a <a
 href="http://www.fields.utoronto.ca/programs/scientific/05-06/profinite">Workshop on Profinite Groups and Applications</a> sponsored by the <a
 href="http://www.fields.utoronto.ca">Fields Institute</a>. </li>
<li>Stuart Margolis and I organized in July 2002 the <a href="http://www.fc.up.pt/cmup/bsteinbg/rf.html">International Conference on Semigroups and Groups in Honor of the 65<sup>th</sup> Birthday of John Rbodes</a>.</li>
